#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/popovers/searchfilterhelp.ui:23
#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/settings/search.ui:143
msgid "Search Result Filters"
msgstr "Filteri rezultata pretrage"

#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/popovers/searchfilterhelp.ui:34
msgid ""
"Search result filters are used to refine which search results are displayed."
msgstr "Filteri rezultata pretrage koriste za sužavanje pretrage."

#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/popovers/searchfilterhelp.ui:43
msgid ""
"Each list of search results has its own filter which can be revealed by "
"toggling the Result Filters button. A filter is made up of multiple fields, "
"all of which are applied when pressing Enter in any one of its fields. "
"Filtering is applied immediately to results already received, and also to "
"those yet to arrive."
msgstr ""
"Svaka otvorena kartica pretrage ima zasebni filter koji se aktivira tipkom "
"Filteri Rezultata. Filter se sastoji od više polja, a sva se primijenjuju "
"tipkom Enter dok ih unosite. Odmah se primjenjuju na trenutne i buduće "
"rezultate pretrage."

#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/popovers/searchfilterhelp.ui:52
msgid ""
"As the name suggests, a search result filter cannot expand your original "
"search, it can only narrow it down. To broaden or change your search terms, "
"perform a new search."
msgstr ""
"Kao što naziv predlaže, filter pretrage samo sužava postojeću pretragu, ne "
"proširuje je. Za proširenje pretrage, prilagodi riječi korištene u "
"tražilici, i pokreni novu pretragu."

#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/popovers/searchfilterhelp.ui:61
msgid "Result Filter Usage"
msgstr "Korištenje filtera"

#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/popovers/searchfilterhelp.ui:73
msgid "Include Text"
msgstr "Sadrži tekst"

#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/popovers/searchfilterhelp.ui:89
msgid "Files, folders and usernames containing this text will be shown."
msgstr "Prikazuje datoteke, mape i korisnike čija imena sadrže unešeni tekst."

#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/popovers/searchfilterhelp.ui:99
msgid ""
"Case is insensitive, but word order is important: 'Instrumental Remix' will "
"not show any 'Remix Instrumental'"
msgstr ""
"Velika slova nisu bitna, ali redoslijed je bitan: \"Instrumental remix\" "
"neće prikazati nazive s \"remix instrumental\""

#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/popovers/searchfilterhelp.ui:109
msgid ""
"Use | (or pipes) to seperate several exact phrases. Example:\n"
"    Remix|Dub Mix|Instrumental"
msgstr ""
"Koristi | (Alt+W) za odvajanje točnih pojmova pretrage. Primjer:\n"
"    Remix|Dub Mix|Instrumental"

#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/popovers/searchfilterhelp.ui:122
msgid "Exclude Text"
msgstr "Izuzmi tekst"

#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/popovers/searchfilterhelp.ui:133
msgid ""
"As above, but files, folders and usernames are filtered out if the text "
"matches."
msgstr "Sakriva datoteke, mape i korisnike čija imena sadrže unešeni tekst."

#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/popovers/searchfilterhelp.ui:154
msgid "Filters files based upon their file extension."
msgstr "Filtrira datoteke prema vrsti."

#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/popovers/searchfilterhelp.ui:164
msgid ""
"Multiple file extensions can be specified, which in turn will reveal more "
"from the list of results. Example:\n"
"    flac wav ape"
msgstr ""
"Moguće je odabrati više vrsta odjednom. Primjer:\n"
"    flac wav mp3"

#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/popovers/searchfilterhelp.ui:175
msgid ""
"It is also possible to invert the filter, specifying file extensions you "
"don't want in your results with an exclamation mark! Example:\n"
"    !mp3 !jpg"
msgstr ""
"Moguće je i izuzeti nešto, naprimjer vrste datoteka koje ne želite započnite "
"s uskličnikom \"!\"\n"
"Primjer: !wav !jpg"

#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/popovers/searchfilterhelp.ui:186
msgid "File Size"
msgstr "Veličina datoteke"

#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/popovers/searchfilterhelp.ui:202
msgid "Filters files based upon their file size."
msgstr "Filtrira datoteke ovisno o veličini."

#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/popovers/searchfilterhelp.ui:212
msgid ""
"By default, the unit used is bytes (B) and files greater than or equal to "
"(>=) the value will be matched."
msgstr ""
"Zadana baza je u byteovima (B) i datoteke koje su jednake ili veće (>=) biti "
"će prikazane."

#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/popovers/searchfilterhelp.ui:222
msgid ""
"Append b, k, m, or g (alternatively kib, mib, or gib) to specify byte, "
"kibibyte, mebibyte, or gibibyte units:\n"
"    20m to show files larger than 20 MiB (mebibytes)."
msgstr ""
"Dodaj oznaku k, m ili g (možeš i kib, mib ili gib) ako trebaš kibibyte, "
"mebibyte ili gigabyte:\n"
"    Primjer: 20m će prikazati samo datoteke veće od 20MiB."

#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/popovers/searchfilterhelp.ui:233
msgid ""
"Prepend = to a value to specify an exact match:\n"
"    =1024 matches files that are exactly 1 KiB (kibibyte)."
msgstr ""
"Predznak \"=\" će vrijednost pretvoriti u točno podudaranje:\n"
"    =1024k prikazuje samo datoteke koje su točno 1MiB (1024 KiB)."

#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/popovers/searchfilterhelp.ui:244
msgid ""
"Prepend ! to a value to exclude files of a specific size:\n"
"    !30.5m to hide files that are 30.5 MiB (mebibytes)."
msgstr ""
"Predznak ! će vrijednost pretvoriti u izuzimanje s liste:\n"
"    !20m će sakriti datoteke koje imaju 20 MiB ili više."

#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/popovers/searchfilterhelp.ui:255
msgid ""
"Prepend < or > to find files smaller/larger than the given value. Use a "
"space between each condition to include a range:\n"
"    >10.5m <1g to show files larger than 10.5 MiB, but smaller than 1 GiB."
msgstr ""
"Predznaci < ili > su za datoteke manje ili veće od zadane vrijednosti. "
"Koristite razmak između pojedine stavke:\n"
"    >10.5m <50m prikazuje datoteke veće od 10.5 MiB a manje od 50 MiB."

#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/popovers/searchfilterhelp.ui:266
msgid ""
"The better-known variants kb, mb, and gb can also be used for kilobyte, "
"megabyte, and gigabyte units."
msgstr "Mogu se koristiti i poznatije varijante: kb, mb i gb."

#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/popovers/searchfilterhelp.ui:294
msgid "Filters files based upon their bitrate."
msgstr "Filtrira datoteke po bitrate-u."

#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/popovers/searchfilterhelp.ui:304
msgid ""
"Values must be entered as numeric digits only. The unit is always Kb/s "
"(Kilobits per second)."
msgstr ""
"Vrijednosti su isključivo brojevi. Baza je uvijek Kb/s (kilobyte po sekundi)."

#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/popovers/searchfilterhelp.ui:314
msgid ""
"Like File Size (above), operators =, !, <, >, <= or >= can be used, and "
"multiple conditions can be specified, for example to show files with a "
"bitrate of at least 256 Kb/s with a maximum bitrate of 1411 Kb/s:\n"
"    256 <=1411"
msgstr ""
"Prihvaćeni su predznaci =, !, <, >, <= ili >= te možeš kombinirati uvjete. "
"Naprimjer:\n"
"    256 <=1411 prikazuje samo datoteke s bitrate-om iznad 256Kbs, a manjim "
"od 1411 Kb/s"

#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/popovers/searchfilterhelp.ui:343
msgid "Filters files based upon their duration."
msgstr "Filtrira datoteke prema trajanju."

#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/popovers/searchfilterhelp.ui:353
msgid ""
"By default, files longer than or equal to (>=) the entered duration will be "
"matched, unless an operator (=, !, <=, < or >) is used."
msgstr ""
"Zadani način je jednako ili duže od unosa (>=), a prihvaćeni su predznaci "
"=, !, <=, < ili > ."

#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/popovers/searchfilterhelp.ui:363
msgid ""
"Enter a raw value in seconds or use the MM:SS and HH:MM:SS time formats:\n"
"    =53 shows files that are around 53 seconds long.\n"
"    >5:30 to show files more than 5 and a half minutes long.\n"
"    <5:30:00 shows files less than 5 and a half hours long."
msgstr ""
"Unesi brojke u sekundama, ili koristi MM:SS i HH:MM:SS format unosa\n"
"   =53 prikazuje datoteke trajanja 53 sekunde.\n"
"   >5:30 prikazuje datoteke dulje od 5 i pol minuta.\n"
"   <5:30:00 prikazuje datoteke kraće od 5 i pol sati."

#: pynicotine/gtkgui/ui/popovers/searchfilterhelp.ui:376
msgid ""
"Multiple conditions can be specified:\n"
"    >6:00 <12:00 to show files between 6 and 12 minutes long.\n"
"    !9:54 !8:43 !7:32 to hide some specific files from the results.\n"
"    =5:34 =4:23 =3:05 to include files with specific durations."
msgstr ""
"Uvjeti se mogu kombinirati:\n"
"    >6:00 <12:00 za prikaz trajanja između 6 i 12 minuta.\n"
"    !9:54 !8:43 !7:32 sakriva datoteke sa specifičnim trajanjem (npr intro "
"špice).\n"
